      <odd id="aspace_a1950e1ed88336133ec0ba1422fbf3f0">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 49 (YRG 49), Papers and projects on Yale.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_96a6f4047f8dd3fc8631f74e7068edf1">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Office of the President, 1974.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
